SearchLight New Tab extension provides you with easiest and most quick search in your new tab and gives you quick access to your last visited sites, right in the comfort of your web browser.

The search features use within the extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing; however, the extension will not make any changes in your default browser search setting. 

By clicking "Add to chrome", you accept and agree to installing SearchLight extension and setting Chrome New Tab search to that provided by the service.
You also agree to the 'End User License Agreement 'and the 'Privacy Policy'.
